  "commentCount": 2,
  "body": "## 🐛 Bug Report\r\n\r\n Open the same file with WPS and Execl, but the height of the line number is different，WPS preview is normal.\r\n用WPS和Execl打开同一个生成的表格，行高不一样，WPS 是正确的。\r\n\r\nLib version: 4.3.0\r\nWPS version：12.1.0.15120\r\nOffice version:  office home and student edition 2019\r\n\r\n\r\n## Execl\r\n<img width=\"696\" alt=\"execl\" src=\"https://github.com/exceljs/exceljs/assets/87855462/637bd633-270e-47e6-9bad-9b69c406081d\">\r\n\r\n## WPS\r\n<img width=\"799\" alt=\"wps\" src=\"https://github.com/exceljs/exceljs/assets/87855462/1aeaffff-81e4-4472-9317-2d90dd55480d\">\r\n\r\n## xlsx\r\n[demo.xlsx](https://github.com/exceljs/exceljs/files/12427284/demo.xlsx)\r\n",
